{"ID":"20220906203856-n2vz1s6","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906203856-n2vz1s6","title":"c-2操作系统","type":"doc","updated":"20220906203856"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203857-fonp9db","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203857-fonp9db","updated":"20220906203857"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.2 操作系统","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203858-74peuc6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203858-74peuc6","updated":"20220906203858"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"操作系统基础","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203859-kzsin4f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203859-kzsin4f","updated":"20220906203859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"面试官顶着蓬松的假发向我走来，只见他一手拿着厚重的 Thinkpad ，一手提着他那淡黄的长裙。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203860-q59yccg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203860-q59yccg","updated":"20220906203860"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是操作系统？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203861-kbb7nrf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203861-kbb7nrf","updated":"20220906203861"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"👨‍💻","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"面试官"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： 先来个简单问题吧！","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"什么是操作系统？"}]},{"ID":"20220906203862-xe8m5xf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203862-xe8m5xf","updated":"20220906203862"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🙋 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：我通过以下四点向您介绍一下什么是操作系统吧！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203863-8e7infv","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203863-8e7infv","updated":"20220906203863"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203864-qvp8jn8","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203864-qvp8jn8","updated":"20220906203864"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203865-m58iwsq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203865-m58iwsq","updated":"20220906203865"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"操作系统（Operating System，简称 OS）是管理计算机硬件与软件资源的程序，是计算机的基石。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203866-b219s4q","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203866-b219s4q","updated":"20220906203866"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203867-haje9w8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203867-haje9w8","updated":"20220906203867"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"操作系统本质上是一个运行在计算机上的软件程序 ，用于管理计算机硬件和软件资源。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 举例：运行在你电脑上的所有应用程序都通过操作系统来调用系统内存以及磁盘等等硬件。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203868-sho15eu","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203868-sho15eu","updated":"20220906203868"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203869-stcu9y9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203869-stcu9y9","updated":"20220906203869"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"操作系统存在屏蔽了硬件层的复杂性。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 操作系统就像是硬件使用的负责人，统筹着各种相关事项。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203870-7rg5f03","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203870-7rg5f03","updated":"20220906203870"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203871-b1m8i9a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203871-b1m8i9a","updated":"20220906203871"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"操作系统的内核（Kernel）是操作系统的核心部分，它负责系统的内存管理，硬件设备的管理，文件系统的管理以及应用程序的管理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。 内核是连接应用程序和硬件的桥梁，决定着系统的性能和稳定性。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203872-owf957w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203872-owf957w","updated":"20220906203872"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Kernel_Layout","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/2020-8/Kernel_Layout.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203873-wdirm6q","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203873-wdirm6q","updated":"20220906203873"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"系统调用","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203874-oamee4q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203874-oamee4q","updated":"20220906203874"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"👨‍💻","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"面试官"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"什么是系统调用呢？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 能不能详细介绍一下。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203875-5389x0x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203875-5389x0x","updated":"20220906203875"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🙋 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：介绍系统调用之前，我们先来了解一下用户态和系统态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203876-bw5zabf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203876-bw5zabf","updated":"20220906203876"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据进程访问资源的特点，我们可以把进程在系统上的运行分为两个级别：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203877-ewksaqt","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203877-ewksaqt","updated":"20220906203877"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203878-o5xh0tf","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203878-o5xh0tf","updated":"20220906203878"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203879-ggjtasp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203879-ggjtasp","updated":"20220906203879"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用户态(user mode) : 用户态运行的进程可以直接读取用户程序的数据。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203880-76rm3pu","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203880-76rm3pu","updated":"20220906203880"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203881-jq1izy6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203881-jq1izy6","updated":"20220906203881"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"系统态(kernel mode):可以简单的理解系统态运行的进程或程序几乎可以访问计算机的任何资源，不受限制。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203882-1x1g3de","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203882-1x1g3de","updated":"20220906203882"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说了用户态和系统态之后，那么什么是系统调用呢？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203883-jrz5hoe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203883-jrz5hoe","updated":"20220906203883"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们运行的程序基本都是运行在用户态，如果我们调用操作系统提供的系统态级别的子功能咋办呢？那就需要系统调用了！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203884-vigfxgu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203884-vigfxgu","updated":"20220906203884"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也就是说在我们运行的用户程序中，凡是与系统态级别的资源有关的操作（如文件管理、进程控制、内存管理等)，都必须通过系统调用方式向操作系统提出服务请求，并由操作系统代为完成。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203885-03tloh5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203885-03tloh5","updated":"20220906203885"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这些系统调用按功能大致可分为如下几类：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203886-bfd8hhd","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203886-bfd8hhd","updated":"20220906203886"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203887-mfcgz64","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203887-mfcgz64","updated":"20220906203887"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203888-u6nb94d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203888-u6nb94d","updated":"20220906203888"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"设备管理。完成设备的请求或释放，以及设备启动等功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203889-9kzkmqu","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203889-9kzkmqu","updated":"20220906203889"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203890-8qtfnq0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203890-8qtfnq0","updated":"20220906203890"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文件管理。完成文件的读、写、创建及删除等功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203891-8hinsak","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203891-8hinsak","updated":"20220906203891"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203892-vs6ly2g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203892-vs6ly2g","updated":"20220906203892"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程控制。完成进程的创建、撤销、阻塞及唤醒等功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203893-xx3cxdh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203893-xx3cxdh","updated":"20220906203893"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203894-s9kbvok","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203894-s9kbvok","updated":"20220906203894"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程通信。完成进程之间的消息传递或信号传递等功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203895-tu845ig","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203895-tu845ig","updated":"20220906203895"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203896-6207pnb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203896-6207pnb","updated":"20220906203896"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"内存管理。完成内存的分配、回收以及获取作业占用内存区大小及地址等功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203897-taczpl4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203897-taczpl4","updated":"20220906203897"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程和线程","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203898-0como02","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203898-0como02","updated":"20220906203898"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程和线程的区别","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203899-5v61qpb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203899-5v61qpb","updated":"20220906203899"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"👨‍💻","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"面试官"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 好的！我明白了！那你再说一下： ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"进程和线程的区别"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203900-v4i33jd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203900-v4i33jd","updated":"20220906203900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🙋 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 好的！ 下图是 Java 内存区域，我们从 JVM 的角度来说一下线程和进程之间的关系吧！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203901-k9yi00d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203901-k9yi00d","updated":"20220906203901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Java 运行时数据区域（JDK1.8 之后）","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/java/jvm/java-runtime-data-areas-jdk1.8.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203902-isv27es","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203902-isv27es","updated":"20220906203902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从上图可以看出：一个进程中可以有多个线程，多个线程共享进程的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"堆"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法区 (JDK1.8 之后的元空间)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"资源，但是每个线程有自己的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"程序计数器"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚拟机栈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本地方法栈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203903-gw0hkfm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203903-gw0hkfm","updated":"20220906203903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"总结："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 线程是进程划分成的更小的运行单位,一个进程在其执行的过程中可以产生多个线程。线程和进程最大的不同在于基本上各进程是独立的，而各线程则不一定，因为同一进程中的线程极有可能会相互影响。线程执行开销小，但不利于资源的管理和保护；而进程正相反。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203904-2e2e2fj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203904-2e2e2fj","updated":"20220906203904"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程有哪几种状态?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203905-2pnw6ts","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203905-2pnw6ts","updated":"20220906203905"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"👨‍💻","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"面试官"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： 那你再说说","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"进程有哪几种状态?"}]},{"ID":"20220906203906-9iokcpu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203906-9iokcpu","updated":"20220906203906"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🙋 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：我们一般把进程大致分为 5 种状态，这一点和","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://github.com/Snailclimb/JavaGuide/blob/master/docs/java/Multithread/JavaConcurrencyBasicsCommonInterviewQuestionsSummary.md#6-%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F%E5%92%8C%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81","TextMarkTextContent":"线程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"很像！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203907-van2psn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203907-van2psn","updated":"20220906203907"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203908-s7b9dk3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203908-s7b9dk3","updated":"20220906203908"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203909-03kh31q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203909-03kh31q","updated":"20220906203909"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"创建状态(new)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：进程正在被创建，尚未到就绪状态。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203910-bl73wq1","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203910-bl73wq1","updated":"20220906203910"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203911-1q5i6sv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203911-1q5i6sv","updated":"20220906203911"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"就绪状态(ready)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：进程已处于准备运行状态，即进程获得了除了处理器之外的一切所需资源，一旦得到处理器资源(处理器分配的时间片)即可运行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203912-wazlbvb","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203912-wazlbvb","updated":"20220906203912"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203913-aeaotu9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203913-aeaotu9","updated":"20220906203913"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"运行状态(running)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：进程正在处理器上上运行(单核 CPU 下任意时刻只有一个进程处于运行状态)。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203914-b75jvuc","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203914-b75jvuc","updated":"20220906203914"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203915-il6ume1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203915-il6ume1","updated":"20220906203915"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"阻塞状态(waiting)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：又称为等待状态，进程正在等待某一事件而暂停运行如等待某资源为可用或等待 IO 操作完成。即使处理器空闲，该进程也不能运行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203916-2h52sbf","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203916-2h52sbf","updated":"20220906203916"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203917-bev38q2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203917-bev38q2","updated":"20220906203917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"结束状态(terminated)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：进程正在从系统中消失。可能是进程正常结束或其他原因中断退出运行。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203918-a8nlq5v","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203918-a8nlq5v","updated":"20220906203918"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203919-8g0yypt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203919-8g0yypt","updated":"20220906203919"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"订正：下图中 running 状态被 interrupt 向 ready 状态转换的箭头方向反了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203920-o2gn8kg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203920-o2gn8kg","updated":"20220906203920"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"process-state","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://my-blog-to-use.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019-11/d38202593012b457debbcd74994c6292.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203921-wd20bqg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203921-wd20bqg","updated":"20220906203921"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程间的通信方式","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203922-rjo09ri","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203922-rjo09ri","updated":"20220906203922"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"👨‍💻","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"面试官"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"进程间的通信常见的的有哪几种方式呢?"}]},{"ID":"20220906203923-9bdntwc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203923-9bdntwc","updated":"20220906203923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🙋 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：大概有 7 种常见的进程间的通信方式。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203924-1zihkbq","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203924-1zihkbq","updated":"20220906203924"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203925-yp5e2ev","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203925-yp5e2ev","updated":"20220906203925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面这部分总结参考了:","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://www.jianshu.com/p/c1015f5ffa74","TextMarkTextContent":"《进程间通信 IPC (InterProcess Communication)》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 这篇文章，推荐阅读，总结的非常不错。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203926-u3wjxbe","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203926-u3wjxbe","updated":"20220906203926"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203927-33fcrwk","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203927-33fcrwk","updated":"20220906203927"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203928-oxxu8hr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203928-oxxu8hr","updated":"20220906203928"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"管道/匿名管道(Pipes)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：用于具有亲缘关系的父子进程间或者兄弟进程之间的通信。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203929-wqlevf0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203929-wqlevf0","updated":"20220906203929"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203930-vzk2918","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203930-vzk2918","updated":"20220906203930"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"有名管道(Names Pipes)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : 匿名管道由于没有名字，只能用于亲缘关系的进程间通信。为了克服这个缺点，提出了有名管道。有名管道严格遵循","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"先进先出(first in first out)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。有名管道以磁盘文件的方式存在，可以实现本机任意两个进程通信。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203931-lnsneah","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203931-lnsneah","updated":"20220906203931"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203932-cr4qajt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203932-cr4qajt","updated":"20220906203932"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"信号(Signal)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：信号是一种比较复杂的通信方式，用于通知接收进程某个事件已经发生；","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203933-3itxsok","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203933-3itxsok","updated":"20220906203933"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203934-ww5r529","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203934-ww5r529","updated":"20220906203934"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"消息队列(Message Queuing)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：消息队列是消息的链表,具有特定的格式,存放在内存中并由消息队列标识符标识。管道和消息队列的通信数据都是先进先出的原则。与管道（无名管道：只存在于内存中的文件；命名管道：存在于实际的磁盘介质或者文件系统）不同的是消息队列存放在内核中，只有在内核重启(即，操作系统重启)或者显式地删除一个消息队列时，该消息队列才会被真正的删除。消息队列可以实现消息的随机查询,消息不一定要以先进先出的次序读取,也可以按消息的类型读取.比 FIFO 更有优势。","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"消息队列克服了信号承载信息量少，管道只能承载无格式字 节流以及缓冲区大小受限等缺点。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203935-oz372lw","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203935-oz372lw","updated":"20220906203935"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203936-n6tdaw8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203936-n6tdaw8","updated":"20220906203936"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"信号量(Semaphores)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：信号量是一个计数器，用于多进程对共享数据的访问，信号量的意图在于进程间同步。这种通信方式主要用于解决与同步相关的问题并避免竞争条件。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203937-pm0r66t","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":6},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203937-pm0r66t","updated":"20220906203937"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203938-iruz0ib","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203938-iruz0ib","updated":"20220906203938"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"共享内存(Shared memory)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：使得多个进程可以访问同一块内存空间，不同进程可以及时看到对方进程中对共享内存中数据的更新。这种方式需要依靠某种同步操作，如互斥锁和信号量等。可以说这是最有用的进程间通信方式。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203939-jglk785","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":7},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203939-jglk785","updated":"20220906203939"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203940-v6xfm2j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203940-v6xfm2j","updated":"20220906203940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"套接字(Sockets)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : 此方法主要用于在客户端和服务器之间通过网络进行通信。套接字是支持 TCP/IP 的网络通信的基本操作单元，可以看做是不同主机之间的进程进行双向通信的端点，简单的说就是通信的两方的一种约定，用套接字中的相关函数来完成通信过程。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203941-xad7bde","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203941-xad7bde","updated":"20220906203941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"线程间的同步的方式","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203942-p2x6jse","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203942-p2x6jse","updated":"20220906203942"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"👨‍💻","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"面试官"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"那线程间的同步的方式有哪些呢?"}]},{"ID":"20220906203943-43tcy1e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203943-43tcy1e","updated":"20220906203943"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🙋 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：线程同步是两个或多个共享关键资源的线程的并发执行。应该同步线程以避免关键的资源使用冲突。操作系统一般有下面三种线程同步的方式：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203944-v43fn7n","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203944-v43fn7n","updated":"20220906203944"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203945-pn82ozj","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203945-pn82ozj","updated":"20220906203945"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203946-ez0xboj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203946-ez0xboj","updated":"20220906203946"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"互斥量(Mutex)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：采用互斥对象机制，只有拥有互斥对象的线程才有访问公共资源的权限。因为互斥对象只有一个，所以可以保证公共资源不会被多个线程同时访问。比如 Java 中的 synchronized 关键词和各种 Lock 都是这种机制。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203947-7ctc0u5","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203947-7ctc0u5","updated":"20220906203947"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203948-hhxeopv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203948-hhxeopv","updated":"20220906203948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"信号量(Semaphore)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：它允许同一时刻多个线程访问同一资源，但是需要控制同一时刻访问此资源的最大线程数量。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203949-ae2r156","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203949-ae2r156","updated":"20220906203949"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203950-fzin7pw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203950-fzin7pw","updated":"20220906203950"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"事件(Event)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" :Wait/Notify：通过通知操作的方式来保持多线程同步，还可以方便的实现多线程优先级的比较操作。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203951-cp8yq7n","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203951-cp8yq7n","updated":"20220906203951"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程的调度算法","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203952-92d69c1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203952-92d69c1","updated":"20220906203952"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"👨‍💻","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"面试官"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"你知道操作系统中进程的调度算法有哪些吗?"}]},{"ID":"20220906203953-jmnur1t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203953-jmnur1t","updated":"20220906203953"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🙋 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：嗯嗯！这个我们大学的时候学过，是一个很重要的知识点！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203954-s65g0w9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203954-s65g0w9","updated":"20220906203954"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了确定首先执行哪个进程以及最后执行哪个进程以实现最大 CPU 利用率，计算机科学家已经定义了一些算法，它们是：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203955-hog7cte","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203955-hog7cte","updated":"20220906203955"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203956-tev8noj","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203956-tev8noj","updated":"20220906203956"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203957-g3sc07n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203957-g3sc07n","updated":"20220906203957"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"先到先服务(FCFS)调度算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : 从就绪队列中选择一个最先进入该队列的进程为之分配资源，使它立即执行并一直执行到完成或发生某事件而被阻塞放弃占用 CPU 时再重新调度。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203958-kf9eekg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203958-kf9eekg","updated":"20220906203958"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203959-uib1a60","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203959-uib1a60","updated":"20220906203959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"短作业优先(SJF)的调度算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : 从就绪队列中选出一个估计运行时间最短的进程为之分配资源，使它立即执行并一直执行到完成或发生某事件而被阻塞放弃占用 CPU 时再重新调度。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203960-5bvx7kg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203960-5bvx7kg","updated":"20220906203960"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203961-449v5nr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203961-449v5nr","updated":"20220906203961"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"时间片轮转调度算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : 时间片轮转调度是一种最古老，最简单，最公平且使用最广的算法，又称 RR(Round robin)调度。每个进程被分配一个时间段，称作它的时间片，即该进程允许运行的时间。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203962-nr0uxyz","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203962-nr0uxyz","updated":"20220906203962"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203963-wpzi6vt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203963-wpzi6vt","updated":"20220906203963"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多级反馈队列调度算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：前面介绍的几种进程调度的算法都有一定的局限性。如","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"短进程优先的调度算法，仅照顾了短进程而忽略了长进程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。多级反馈队列调度算法既能使高优先级的作业得到响应又能使短作业（进程）迅速完成。，因而它是目前","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"被公认的一种较好的进程调度算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，UNIX 操作系统采取的便是这种调度算法。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203964-875a187","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203964-875a187","updated":"20220906203964"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203965-ir3iiy0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203965-ir3iiy0","updated":"20220906203965"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"优先级调度"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： 为每个流程分配优先级，首先执行具有最高优先级的进程，依此类推。具有相同优先级的进程以 FCFS 方式执行。可以根据内存要求，时间要求或任何其他资源要求来确定优先级。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203966-cnwb6aw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203966-cnwb6aw","updated":"20220906203966"},